{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "financial-control-api-v1",
    "name": "Financial Control API - Autenticaçăo JWT",
    "description": "Collection completa da API de Controle Financeiro com autenticaçăo JWT, multi-tenancy e soft delete.\n\n## Como usar:\n\n1. **Registrar** um usuário (Auth ? Register)\n2. **Login** para obter o token (Auth ? Login)\n3. O token será **salvo automaticamente** na variável `authToken`\n4. Use as outras rotas normalmente (já văo usar o token)\n\n## Variáveis da Collection:\n\n- `baseUrl`: http://localhost:5296\n- `authToken`: (preenchido automaticamente após login)\n\n## Endpoints:\n\n- **Auth**: Register, Login\n- **CreditCard**: CRUD completo + Expenses\n- **User**: CRUD de usuários\n- **Soft Delete**: Restaurar dados deletados",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "?? Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "// Salvar token automaticamente",
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set(\"authToken\", jsonData.token);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set(\"userId\", jsonData.userId);",
                  "    console.log(\"? Token salvo:\", jsonData.token.substring(0, 20) + \"...\");",
                  "    console.log(\"? UserId salvo:\", jsonData.userId);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Lucas Alves\",\n  \"email\": \"lucas@dev.com\",\n  \"password\": \"SenhaSegura123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "auth",
                "register"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Registra um novo usuário no sistema.\n\n**Corpo da requisiçăo:**\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"Nome do Usuário\",\n  \"email\": \"email@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"senha123\"\n}\n```\n\n**Resposta:**\n```json\n{\n  \"userId\": 1,\n  \"name\": \"Nome do Usuário\",\n  \"email\": \"email@example.com\",\n  \"token\": \"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIs...\",\n  \"role\": \"User\"\n}\n```\n\n?? O token é salvo automaticamente na variável `authToken`"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "// Salvar token automaticamente",
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set(\"authToken\", jsonData.token);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set(\"userId\", jsonData.userId);",
                  "    console.log(\"? Token salvo:\", jsonData.token.substring(0, 20) + \"...\");",
                  "    console.log(\"? UserId salvo:\", jsonData.userId);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"lucas@dev.com\",\n  \"password\": \"SenhaSegura123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "auth",
                "login"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Faz login com usuário existente.\n\n**Corpo da requisiçăo:**\n```json\n{\n  \"email\": \"email@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"senha123\"\n}\n```\n\n**Resposta:**\n```json\n{\n  \"userId\": 1,\n  \"name\": \"Nome do Usuário\",\n  \"email\": \"email@example.com\",\n  \"token\": \"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIs...\",\n  \"role\": \"User\"\n}\n```\n\n?? O token é salvo automaticamente na variável `authToken`"
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ],
      "description": "Endpoints de autenticaçăo (Register e Login).\n\n? O token JWT é salvo automaticamente após register/login."
